A limited binary build of GCC, for bootstrapping your ‘real’ GCC
installation, possibly with Ada support.

The binary was made in some fashion similar to the following:

tar xf /path/to/gcc-4.7.4.tar.bz2
mkdir gcc-4.7.4-build
cd gcc-4.7.4-build
sh /path/to/CONFIGURE-gnat-bootstrap-4.7.4.sh
make
make install-strip
chown -Rv root:root /opt/gnat-bootstrap-4.7
tar -C / opt/gnat-bootstrap-4.7 -c -v --xz -f /path/to/gnat-bootstrap-4.7-4.7.4.tar.xz
